# User Module

## Register a new user
```dart
var headers = {
  'Content-Type': 'application/x-www-form-urlencoded'
};
var request = http.Request('POST', Uri.parse('https://realtys-api.herokuapp.com/api/realtys/signUp'));
request.bodyFields = {
  'firstName': 'Adelabou',
  'name': 'imdad',
  'email': 'adelaboukiss@gmail.com',
  'phoneNumber': '97018954',
  'password': 'avatarimdad96',
  'isAgent': 'true'
};
request.headers.addAll(headers);

http.StreamedResponse response = await request.send();

if (response.statusCode == 200) {
  print(await response.stream.bytesToString());
}
else {
  print(response.reasonPhrase);
}
```
> This is the response we should get:

```json
{
    "msg": "user created well"
}
```

### Request Information
|Category|Value|
|---------|--------|
|Http request| `POST`|
|URL|https://realtys-api.herokuapp.com/api/realtys/signUp|

### Headers
No headers required

### Input Schema for requests
|Field|Meaning|
|-----|--------|
|firstName| firstname of the user
|name| name of the user
|phoneNumber| phonenumber of the user
|password| password of the user
|isAgent| A boolean to know if the user is registered as an advertiser or not. Defaults to `false`

### Output Schema of request
|Field|Meaning|
|-----|--------|
|status| return `201` if the user has registered|
|msg| The result of the request|

